 -- Karen was late to the bus stop, but fortunately the bus was delayed as well.
 -- 凯伦到公交车站的时候已经晚了，但幸好那辆公交也晚点了。

在这些条目还发现' fortunately '：
在英文解释里：
as luck would have it - fortuitously - good thing - mercifully - thankfully
中文：
幸好 - 有幸

标题中含有单词 'fortunately' 的论坛讨论：

Fortunately, I had a rain jacket on.

acceptability of Fortunately + will

Accidentally - fortunately

Fortunately for all chocolate lovers

Fortunately for us, the weather changed.

Fortunately he can't be elected

fortunately it's being restored now

fortunately you failed to "steal" a parking space

Fortunately/luckily

I know not whether any war ever succeeded so fortunately in all its events but

I was fortunate to... vs fortunately, I could... (any difference?)

unfortunately / fortunately for somebody

who fortunately speaks fluent siren.

